         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="CompositionOldTestament" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet160#ms_i1.25">
               <t:ab>
                  <t:pb n="32ra"/>
           ወኦሪት፡ ዘልደት፡ ወኦሪት፡ ዘጸአት፡ ወመጽሐፈ፡ ኩፋሌ፡ ጸሐፈ፡ መልአከ፡
           ገጽ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ወልድ፡ ዋኀድ፡ <t:supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">ወ</t:supplied>ወሀቦ፡ ለሙሴ።
         </t:ab>
            </t:div>
       
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Stars" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet160#ms_i1.36">
               <t:ab>
                  <t:pb n="54rb"/>
           እስመ፡ ፩፡ ሰዓት፡ በሐሳበ፡ ጸሓይ፡ ወወርኅ፡ ፭፡ ኪክሮከ፡ ወበኀሳበ፡ ከዋክብት፡ ፩፡ ሰዓት፡ ፲ወ፭፡ ኪክሮስ።
         </t:ab>
            </t:div>
       
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Metropolitans1" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet160#ms_i2.15">
               <t:ab>
          አባ፡ ሚናስ፡ ዓዲ፡ አባ፡ አብርሃም፡ ወአባ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወምስሌሆሙ፡ ፴ወ፯፡ ጳጳሳት፡ ዘኢተዐውቀ፡ ስሞሙ፡
         </t:ab>
            </t:div>
       
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Metropolitans2" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet160#ms_i2.15">
               <t:ab>
           ተቀብሩ፡ በአክሱም፡ ፭፡ <t:sic resp="PRS10747Zotenbe">ድኅሬሆ።</t:sic> አባ፡ በርተሎሜዎስ፡ ዘተቀብረ፡ በሀገራይ፡ ወ፮፡ ተቀብሩ፡ በናዝሬት።
         </t:ab>
            </t:div>
       
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Metropolitans3" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet160#ms_i2.15">
               <t:ab>
           ዘተመይጠ፡ ኢየሩሳሌም፡ 
         </t:ab>
            </t:div>
       
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="Metropolitans4" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet160#ms_i2.15">
               <t:ab>
         ፲ወ፯፡ ዘተቀብረ፡ ቁሶ፡
         </t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
